    <title>关于程序WindowsCleaner</title>
    <url>/2023/07/20/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8FWindowsCleaner/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="引言"><a href="#引言" class="headerlink" title="引言"></a>引言</h2><p>C盘爆满，想开发一个程序来清理一下垃圾，于是就做出了它</p>
<h2 id="粗略剖析原理"><a href="#粗略剖析原理" class="headerlink" title="粗略剖析原理"></a>粗略剖析原理</h2><p>正文：</p>
<ol>
<li><p>引入必要的头文件<br>在程序开头，我们引入了一些必要的头文件，包括<code>&lt;iostream&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;windows.h&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;shellapi.h&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;shlobj.h&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;string&gt;</code>和<code>&lt;vector&gt;</code>。这些头文件提供了我们所需的函数和数据结构，以便与WindowsAPI进行交互。</p>
</li>
<li><p>清理系统盘temp文件夹<br>我们首先介绍的是清理系统盘的临时文件夹功能。通过调用<code>GetTempPathW</code>函数获取系统的临时文件夹路径，然后使用<code>calculateDirectorySize</code>函数计算该文件夹的总大小。接下来，我们使用<code>cleanDirectory</code>函数清理临时文件夹，并将清理的文件大小打印出来。</p>
</li>
<li><p>删除回收站文件<br>通过调用<code>SHEmptyRecycleBin</code>函数，我们可以删除回收站中的所有文件。该函数接受一些标志参数，我们使用<code>SHERB_NOCONFIRMATION | SHERB_NOPROGRESSUI | SHERB_NOSOUND</code>来禁用</p>
</li>
<li><p>清理QQ和微信缓存<br>我们定义了一个<code>cleanCache</code>函数，用于清理指定路径下的缓存文件。该函数使用<code>calculateDirectorySize</code>函数计算缓存目录的总大小，并调用<code>cleanDirectory</code>函数清理缓存目录。最后，我们打印出清理的缓存大小。</p>
</li>
<li><p>查找磁盘中大文件<br>我们定义了一个<code>findLargeFiles</code>函数，用于在指定路径下查找大于指定阈值的文件。该函数使用<code>calculateDirectorySize</code>函数计算目录的总大小，并与阈值比较。如果目录大小超过阈值，则将文件路径添加到一个<code>vector</code>中。在递归调用时，我们使用<code>findLargeFiles</code>函数遍历子目录并查找大文件。最后，我们将找到的大文件路径打印出来。</p>
</li>
<li><p>主函数<br>在主函数中，我们使用一个无限循环来提供菜单选项。用户可以选择不同的功能，包括清理系统盘temp文件夹、删除回收站文件、清理QQ缓存、清理微信缓存和查找磁盘中大文件。根据用户的选择，我们调用相应的函数来执行相应的操作。最后，用户可以选择退出程序。</p>
<h2 id="附录"><a href="#附录" class="headerlink" title="附录"></a>附录</h2><p>代码源码：</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="C++"><figure class="iseeu highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;windows.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;shellapi.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;shlobj.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">cleanDirectory</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> wstring&amp; directory, ULONGLONG&amp; totalSize)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    WIN32_FIND_DATAW findData;</span><br><span class="line">    HANDLE hFind = <span class="built_in">FindFirstFileW</span>((directory + <span class="string">L&quot;\\*&quot;</span>).<span class="built_in">c_str</span>(), &amp;findData);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (hFind != INVALID_HANDLE_VALUE) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">do</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">const</span> wstring fileName = findData.cFileName;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (fileName != <span class="string">L&quot;.&quot;</span> &amp;&amp; fileName != <span class="string">L&quot;..&quot;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">const</span> wstring fullPath = directory + <span class="string">L&quot;\\&quot;</span> + fileName;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (findData.dwFileAttributes &amp; FILE_ATTRIBUTE_DIRECTORY) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="built_in">cleanDirectory</span>(fullPath, totalSize);</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="built_in">RemoveDirectoryW</span>(fullPath.<span class="built_in">c_str</span>());</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    ULONGLONG fileSize = <span class="built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;ULONGLONG&gt;(findData.nFileSizeLow) +</span><br><span class="line">                        (<span class="built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;ULONGLONG&gt;(findData.nFileSizeHigh) &lt;&lt; <span class="number">32</span>);</span><br><span class="line">                    totalSize += fileSize;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="built_in">DeleteFileW</span>(fullPath.<span class="built_in">c_str</span>());</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="built_in">FindNextFileW</span>(hFind, &amp;findData));</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">FindClose</span>(hFind);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">ULONGLONG <span class="title">calculateDirectorySize</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> wstring&amp; directory)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ULONGLONG totalSize = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    WIN32_FIND_DATAW findData;</span><br><span class="line">    HANDLE hFind = <span class="built_in">FindFirstFileW</span>((directory + <span class="string">L&quot;\\*&quot;</span>).<span class="built_in">c_str</span>(), &amp;findData);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (hFind != INVALID_HANDLE_VALUE) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">do</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">const</span> wstring fileName = findData.cFileName;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (fileName != <span class="string">L&quot;.&quot;</span> &amp;&amp; fileName != <span class="string">L&quot;..&quot;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">const</span> wstring fullPath = directory + <span class="string">L&quot;\\&quot;</span> + fileName;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (!(findData.dwFileAttributes &amp; FILE_ATTRIBUTE_DIRECTORY)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    ULONGLONG fileSize = <span class="built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;ULONGLONG&gt;(findData.nFileSizeLow) +</span><br><span class="line">                        (<span class="built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;ULONGLONG&gt;(findData.nFileSizeHigh) &lt;&lt; <span class="number">32</span>);</span><br><span class="line">                    totalSize += fileSize;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    totalSize += <span class="built_in">calculateDirectorySize</span>(fullPath);  <span class="comment">// 递归计算子目录大小</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="built_in">FindNextFileW</span>(hFind, &amp;findData));</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">FindClose</span>(hFind);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> totalSize;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">cleanCache</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> wstring&amp; cachePath, <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">wchar_t</span>* cacheName)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ULONGLONG totalSize = <span class="built_in">calculateDirectorySize</span>(cachePath);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cleanDirectory</span>(cachePath, totalSize);</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;已清理&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; cacheName &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;缓存大小: &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; totalSize / (<span class="number">1024</span> * <span class="number">1024</span>) &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; MB\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">emptyRecycleBin</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">SHEmptyRecycleBin</span>(<span class="literal">NULL</span>, <span class="literal">NULL</span>, SHERB_NOCONFIRMATION | SHERB_NOPROGRESSUI | SHERB_NOSOUND);</span><br><span class="line">    ULONGLONG recycleBinSize = <span class="built_in">calculateDirectorySize</span>(<span class="string">L&quot;C:\\$Recycle.Bin&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;已清理文件大小: &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; recycleBinSize / (<span class="number">1024</span> * <span class="number">1024</span>) &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; MB\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">vector&lt;wstring&gt; <span class="title">findLargeFiles</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> wstring&amp; directory, ULONGLONG thresholdSize)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    vector&lt;wstring&gt; largeFiles;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    WIN32_FIND_DATAW findData;</span><br><span class="line">    HANDLE hFind = <span class="built_in">FindFirstFileW</span>((directory + <span class="string">L&quot;\\*&quot;</span>).<span class="built_in">c_str</span>(), &amp;findData);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (hFind != INVALID_HANDLE_VALUE) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">do</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">const</span> wstring fileName = findData.cFileName;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (fileName != <span class="string">L&quot;.&quot;</span> &amp;&amp; fileName != <span class="string">L&quot;..&quot;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">const</span> wstring fullPath = directory + <span class="string">L&quot;\\&quot;</span> + fileName;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (!(findData.dwFileAttributes &amp; FILE_ATTRIBUTE_DIRECTORY)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    ULONGLONG fileSize = <span class="built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;ULONGLONG&gt;(findData.nFileSizeLow) +</span><br><span class="line">                        (<span class="built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;ULONGLONG&gt;(findData.nFileSizeHigh) &lt;&lt; <span class="number">32</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">if</span> (fileSize &gt;= thresholdSize) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        largeFiles.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(fullPath);</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    vector&lt;wstring&gt; subLargeFiles = <span class="built_in">findLargeFiles</span>(fullPath, thresholdSize);  <span class="comment">// 递归查找子目录中的大文件</span></span><br><span class="line">                    largeFiles.<span class="built_in">insert</span>(largeFiles.<span class="built_in">end</span>(), subLargeFiles.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(), subLargeFiles.<span class="built_in">end</span>());</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="built_in">FindNextFileW</span>(hFind, &amp;findData));</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">FindClose</span>(hFind);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> largeFiles;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="literal">true</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> choice;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Windows Cleaner - 清理垃圾文件和软件缓存\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;以下为可选功能\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;1. 清理系统盘temp文件夹（无风险）\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;2. 删除回收站文件\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;3. 清理QQ缓存\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;4. 清理微信缓存\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;5. 查找磁盘中大文件\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;6. 退出\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;请输入:\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        cin &gt;&gt; choice;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (choice == <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">wchar_t</span> tempPath[MAX_PATH];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">GetTempPathW</span>(MAX_PATH, tempPath);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="function">wstring <span class="title">tempDir</span><span class="params">(tempPath)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">            ULONGLONG totalSize = <span class="built_in">calculateDirectorySize</span>(tempDir);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cleanDirectory</span>(tempDir, totalSize);</span><br><span class="line">            totalSize /= (<span class="number">1024</span> * <span class="number">1024</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;已清理文件大小: &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; totalSize &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; MB\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (choice == <span class="number">2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">emptyRecycleBin</span>();</span><br><span class="line">            cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;回收站已清空\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (choice == <span class="number">3</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cleanCache</span>(<span class="string">L&quot;C:\\Tencent\\QQ\\QQBrowser\\Cache&quot;</span>, <span class="string">L&quot;QQ&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (choice == <span class="number">4</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cleanCache</span>(<span class="string">L&quot;C:\\Tencent\\WeChat\\Cache&quot;</span>, <span class="string">L&quot;微信&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (choice == <span class="number">5</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            ULONGLONG thresholdSize;</span><br><span class="line">            cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;请输入要搜索的文件大小阈值（以兆字节为单位）:\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            cin &gt;&gt; thresholdSize;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            thresholdSize *= (<span class="number">1024</span> * <span class="number">1024</span>); <span class="comment">// 将输入的兆字节转换为字节</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            wstring drivePath;</span><br><span class="line">            cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;请输入要搜索的磁盘路径（如C:\\）:\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            cin.<span class="built_in">ignore</span>();  <span class="comment">// 忽略之前的换行符</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">getline</span>(wcin, drivePath);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            vector&lt;wstring&gt; largeFiles = <span class="built_in">findLargeFiles</span>(drivePath, thresholdSize);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (!largeFiles.<span class="built_in">empty</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;以下是大于等于指定阈值的文件:\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; filePath : largeFiles) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    wcout &lt;&lt; filePath &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;未找到大于等于指定阈值的文件\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (choice == <span class="number">6</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
